<div id="content">
    <div class="brspacer">
        <h1>Country ladder</h1><br>
        <div id="pagepath"><a href="/">Naruto Arena</a> &gt; <a href="/ladders/">Ladders</a> &gt; <h2>Country ladder
            </h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="brspacer">
        <b>Note:</b> in order to let your <a href="/profile/" class="con" title="account">account</a> have influence on
        this <a href="/the-ninja-ladder/" class="con" title="ladder">ladder</a> you should confirm that you've selected
        the right country in your <a href="/profile/" class="con" title="profile">profile</a>. If you want to edit your
        <a href="/profile/" class="con" title="profile">profile</a>, then select change settings in your control panel.
        <div class="brspacer">
            Every country that has at least 10 active players automatically competes in this <a
                href="/the-ninja-ladder/" class="con" title="ladder">ladder</a>. If you want to know the most important
            factor on how this <a href="/the-ninja-ladder/" class="con" title="ladder">ladder</a> is formed re<a
                href="/profile/" class="con" title="member">member</a> that this <a href="/the-ninja-ladder/"
                class="con" title="ladder">ladder</a> looks at the top 10 players of every country. The total number of
            players in a country minus the average ladderrank of the top 10 players is used to calculate the country's
            points. (formula: amount of points = total players - average ladderrank)
        </div>

        <div class="brspacer">


        </div>

        <div class="brspacer">
            <table class="maxnb">
                <% if (countryLadder && countryLadder.length> 0) { %>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="title">
                            <td width="3%" class="center">Rank</td>
                            <td width="3%"></td>
                            <td width="38%">&nbsp;Country</td>
                            <td width="30%" class="right"># Players&nbsp;</td>
                            <td width="16%">&nbsp;# Points</td>
                        </tr>
                        <% countryLadder.forEach(function(country, index) { %>
                            <tr class="<%= (index % 2 === 0) ? 'color1' : 'color2' %>" valign="bottom">
                                <td class="lrank">#<%= index + 1 %>
                                </td>
                                <td><img src="/images/countries/<%= country.name.replace(/ /g, '-') %>.gif"
                                        class="licon"></td>
                                <td>
                                    <%= country.name %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="right"><b>
                                        <%= country.playerCount %> players
                                    </b></td>
                                <td><u>
                                        <%= Math.round(country.points) %> points
                                    </u></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="5" class="dots"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }); %>
        </tbody>
    <% } else { %>
        <tbody>
            <tr class="title">
                <td width="100%" class="center" colspan="5">Status</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="color1">
                <td colspan="5" class="center">No countries currently qualify for the ladder (minimum 10
                    active players required).</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    <% } %>
</table>

        </div>
        <div class="brspacer">
        </div>
    </div>
